        h2 Principles
        p
          | Bridging the gap between values and practices are principles. Principles are domain-specific guidelines for life.
        p
          a.btn.btn-dark(href='/principles') View details »
      .col-lg-4
        img.bd-placeholder-img.rounded-circle(width='140' height='140' src="/images/practices.jpg" aria-label='Principles' preserveAspectRatio='xMidYMid slice' focusable='false')
